light enough to sustain us 
the threeday meeting was called after fundamentalists last june 
won denominational rule for the 10th straight year 
they insist on a literal view of the bible as inerrant 
free of error historically scientifically and religiously 
moderates allow for diverse interpretations 
the fundamentalist wing gradually has gained sway over church 
