program through which various agencies are financed 
several particpants favored continued support for that unified 
budget but also creation of foundations to finance causes not 
backed by the denomination but deemed important to moderates 
others favored designated giving only to chosen 
denominational programs with moderates putting other funds in 
escrow until fundamentalists agree to political changes in bylaws 
that enable factional control 
the proposals were to be considered at an alliance board meeting 
scheduled for nov 2829 in charlotte nc 
